metadata.description: Historical percentage of S&P 500 stocks above their moving averages

interpretation.above_70_percent: Strong market with broad participation - most stocks in uptrend
interpretation.below_50_percent: Weak market - more stocks in downtrend than uptrend
interpretation.below_30_percent: Very weak market - most stocks in downtrend, potential oversold
interpretation.200_day_ma: Measures long-term trend strength (bull vs bear market)

field_descriptions.count_above: Number of stocks trading above their moving average
field_descriptions.percentage_above: Percentage of stocks trading above their moving average
